metadata.title: Honey-Can-Do Holiday Decorations Storage Box with Handles, Red SFT-09191 Red
features: Twelve compartments sized for nutcrackers, train sets, and other tall figurines
Dividers and pull-out drawer customize a secure space for precious keepsakes
A dozen satin bags are included for an extra layer of support for fragile items
Peek at contents with clear-view lid and side panel, plus clear label slot
Handles for easy carrying when it’s time to unpack and pack up the decorations
description: When it’s time for an army of nutcrackers to waltz off a fireplace mantle and march into a dark expanse of a storage closet, this is Christmas ornament box those toy soldiers need. Its 12 compartments are especially designed for taller ornaments, like nutcrackers, or snowmen, ceramic Christmas trees, train sets, or any other figurine whose heights excludes them from standard ornament boxes. Moveable divider inserts and a sliding drawer let you customize a safe packing space for your figurines’ requirements; and the clear-view panels allow you to check in on them, making sure they’re not up to any mischief.
